            "heading": "Order Processing Time",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Custom Decorated Merchandise:<br/>Design Creation: 5–8 business days to develop and finalize your logo on the selected product.<br/>Production: Once the design is approved, production and shipping preparation typically take an additional 5–8 business days.<br/><br/>Important: Large quantity orders may require additional lead time.</p>",
