            "heading": "Standard Ground Shipping Rates:",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Shipping is calculated at checkout.<br/>Orders exceeding 576 units will receive a shipping quote for approval.<br/>(Excludes HI, PR, AK – subject to change)</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_DhFXP9": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Payment Methods",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Visa, MasterCard, Discover, American Express<br/>Apple Pay, PayPal, Zelle, Pre-paid money orders, Cashier’s checks<br/>Company checks (must clear before processing)<br/>Wire transfers for international orders<br/><br/>Note:<br/>No CODs.<br/>Credit cards issued outside the U.S. are not accepted.<br/>Schools & government agencies: Purchase orders are no longer accepted.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_MMQcVd": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Custom Decorated Items",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<h1>Returns, Cancellations & Custom Order Policy</h1><p>At CustomizedWear.com, every order is custom made specifically for you. Because your hats and apparel are personalized with your approved logo, artwork, colors, and decoration selections, custom products are non-returnable and non-refundable once production begins.</p><p>Customer satisfaction is extremely important to us, and we will always do our best to resolve legitimate issues fairly and promptly.</p><h2>Sample Recommendation</h2><p>We strongly recommend ordering a blank sample from CapWholesalers.com before placing a large custom order. This allows you to review the fit, color, material, and overall style prior to decoration.</p><p>Since decorated merchandise is custom made and non-returnable once production begins, ordering a sample first can help ensure you are completely satisfied with your selection.</p><h2>Artwork & Order Approval</h2><p>Before production begins, all artwork, digital proofs, mockups, stitch-outs, style selections, colors, quantities, and decoration details must be carefully reviewed and approved by the customer.</p><p>Once style, color, quantity, and artwork approvals are confirmed, no changes or cancellations can be made.</p><p>Because materials, production scheduling, and setup begin quickly after an order is placed, cancellation requests submitted after the order is received may be subject to a 20% restocking and processing fee, even if production has not yet started.</p><h2>Custom Decorated Merchandise</h2><p>Once production begins, all custom embroidered, screen-printed, and patch-decorated merchandise is considered final sale.</p><p>Returns, exchanges, or refunds are not accepted unless:</p><ul><li><br/>The item was damaged or defective<br/></li><li><br/>The wrong item, size, color, or decoration was produced<br/></li><li><br/>The finished product does not reasonably match the approved proof or sample image<br/></li></ul><p>Please note that slight variations in thread colors, patch materials, garment shades, sizing, or logo placement are considered normal within the custom apparel industry and are not considered defects.</p><h2>Reporting an Issue</h2><p>If there is a problem with your order, please contact us within 10 days of delivery.</p><p>📧 <a>info@customizedwear.com</a></p><p>Please include:</p><ul><li><br/>Your order number<br/></li><li><br/>A description of the issue<br/></li><li><br/>Photos showing the problem<br/></li></ul><p>Our team will review the issue promptly and may offer a replacement, correction, store credit, partial refund, or another appropriate resolution depending on the situation.</p><p>We typically respond to customer service inquiries within 1 business day.</p><h2>Shipping & Production</h2><p>Production and delivery times may vary depending on decoration method, order size, artwork approval timing, product availability, and seasonal demand.</p><p>Shipping and handling charges are non-refundable.</p><p>Customers are responsible for providing accurate shipping information during checkout. We are not responsible for delays caused by shipping carriers, weather conditions, or incorrect addresses provided by the customer.</p><h2>Product Availability & Backorders</h2><p>Occasionally, inventory availability may change after an order is placed. If an item becomes unavailable or backordered, we will contact you with available options before proceeding with production.</p><h2>Pricing</h2><p>All prices are subject to change without notice.</p><h2>Return Address</h2><p>Hatco International<br/><br/>Attn: Returns Department<br/><br/>12530 Wiles Rd<br/><br/>Coral Springs, FL 33076</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
